<h1>QuantumEEGNet EDU Edition — Fully Gamified Hybrid Storyboard Experience</h1>
<p>📱 Enhanced Interactive Flow with Visual Avatars, Cinematics, and Split-Screen Mode</p>
<p>This ultimate version integrates visual avatar animations, a celebratory end-of-journey cinematic, and split-screen support for teacher-student interactions on tablets.</p>

<h2>Key New Features</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Visual Avatar Animations
    <ul>
      <li>Each student’s avatar animates (wave, jump, glow) when they add or edit a journal entry.</li>
      <li>Avatars appear as small circular tokens on the edges of the active card.</li>
      <li>Collaborative reflections display avatars in real-time as contributors.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>End-of-Journey Cinematic
    <ul>
      <li>Triggered when all phases + shared reflection are marked complete.</li>
      <li>Visual sequence: Confetti and badge animations fill the screen; Class avatars orbit the 🌎 and assemble into a Hall of Fame frame; 🎵 Musical fanfare with voiceover.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Split-Screen Tablet Mode
    <ul>
      <li>Left Panel: Student journal carousel (vertical + horizontal hybrid)</li>
      <li>Right Panel: Teacher coaching dashboard with heatmaps, tips, real-time journal visibility.</li>
      <li>Teachers can drop encouraging stickers or badges directly into student screens.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

